  "texts": [
    "It provides an advanced analysis tool in the Data-rich world where we are living thanks to the advancement of measurement and communication technologies.",
    "[33] to 2023 [34].The GAI, often referred to as creative AI, constitutes a subset of machine learning techniques that leverage multi-layer ANNs to handle intricate patterns.",
    "Beyond traditional learning, GAI possesses the ability to generate diverse media, including text and images, based on the available data.",
    "GAI models undergo training, wherein they grasp the patterns and structures of the input data through neural network machine learning techniques applied to extensive language models.",
    "Consequently, they generate novel data with analogous characteristics [35]."
  ]
}